UniLib
======

UniLib is a simple C++11 Unicode library.

If currently offers:
- utf-8 and utf-16 encodings
- Unicode General Category info
- simple uppercasing and lowercasing
- normalization forms

The library consists of self contained source code in unilib directory.
No build system is provided.

Copyright 2014 by Institute of Formal and Applied Linguistics, Faculty of
Mathematics and Physics, Charles University in Prague, Czech Republic.

UniLib repository http://github.com/ufal/unilib is hosted on GitHub.
